{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-tutorial-js","path":"/tutorial/write-narration","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>本章将带您了解文稿的全部功能和细节。</p>\n<p>首先，文稿在这里相当于是<strong>旁白</strong>，或者说是<strong>解说</strong>。\n也就是，视频的播放会完全由文稿的进度来决定的。\n所以，文稿一旦确定了，对应的时间轴中每个词出现的时间点也就确定了。</p>\n<p>而光标所在的位置，代表当前画面和字幕的时间点。</p>\n<h2>播放预览</h2>\n<p>点击最上面的两个播放按钮，分别是从本段开始播放、从头开始播放。\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 523px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/animeBoard/static/58dcbcda28ec8e148363fd497eca15e4/8df40/playButtons.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 64%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"playButtons\"\n        title=\"playButtons\"\n        src=\"/animeBoard/static/58dcbcda28ec8e148363fd497eca15e4/8df40/playButtons.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/animeBoard/static/58dcbcda28ec8e148363fd497eca15e4/e07e9/playButtons.jpg 200w,\n/animeBoard/static/58dcbcda28ec8e148363fd497eca15e4/066f9/playButtons.jpg 400w,\n/animeBoard/static/58dcbcda28ec8e148363fd497eca15e4/8df40/playButtons.jpg 523w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 523px) 100vw, 523px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>点击每一段落上面的播放按钮就可以预览本段。\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 190px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/animeBoard/static/a9926eea2a9a0210c7070ab5e842001c/82f15/blockPlayButton.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 47.89473684210526%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"blockPlayButton\"\n        title=\"blockPlayButton\"\n        src=\"/animeBoard/static/a9926eea2a9a0210c7070ab5e842001c/82f15/blockPlayButton.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/animeBoard/static/a9926eea2a9a0210c7070ab5e842001c/82f15/blockPlayButton.jpg 190w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 190px) 100vw, 190px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>字幕</h2>\n<p>可以在写文稿的同时，直接把右上角字幕的按钮打开，就直接在画面中看到字幕了。\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 238px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/animeBoard/static/cb97be4a124329967a9dc4fb76cbd675/7ec08/subtitleButton.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 31.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"subtitleButton\"\n        title=\"subtitleButton\"\n        src=\"/animeBoard/static/cb97be4a124329967a9dc4fb76cbd675/7ec08/subtitleButton.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/animeBoard/static/cb97be4a124329967a9dc4fb76cbd675/e07e9/subtitleButton.jpg 200w,\n/animeBoard/static/cb97be4a124329967a9dc4fb76cbd675/7ec08/subtitleButton.jpg 238w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 238px) 100vw, 238px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>语言</h2>\n<p>支持英文和中文。也就是，它会根据文稿中，中文数量的比例、英文数量的比例，来决定着该文稿的语言。\n也就是，不同的文稿可以是不同的语言。这决定着，机器念文稿，以及录音对齐时所采用的语言。</p>\n<p>另外，文稿的语言和软件的语言无关。软件的语言在一台电脑上，会一直是一种。</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"March 09, 2021","slug":"/tutorial/write-narration","title":"写文稿"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/tutorial/write-narration"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}